{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Community knowledge program · OIATC{% endblock %}
{% block description %}OIATC's community knowledge program: plain-language explainers for members, on treaty annuities, the Massey solar project, where data lives, and responsible AI in coursework. A local reporter used the Massey explainer.{% endblock %}
{% block og_title %}Community knowledge program{% endblock %}
{% block og_description %}Plain-language explainers for members: treaty annuities, the solar project, where data lives, responsible AI in coursework. A local reporter used the Massey explainer.{% endblock %}
{% block body_class %}route-program-community-knowledge{% endblock %}

{% block head_styles %}{% include 'partials/funder-styles.html.twig' %}{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<article class="fund-wrap fund-wrap--narrow">

  <p class="fund-eyebrow">OIATC program</p>
  <h1>Community knowledge</h1>
  <p class="fund-lede">Plain-language civic information for members. We take the documents and decisions that affect a community and turn them into explainers anyone can read, every claim sourced, updated as the picture changes.</p>

  <div class="fund-body">
    <p>These are living resources, not one-off posts. A news system tracks updates and feeds each explainer's latest changes. A local reporter covering the project used the Massey explainer, which is the kind of reach this program is built for.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="fund-sec">
    <h2>The work, by stage</h2>
    <ul class="fund-links">
      <li><span class="fund-stage fund-stage--live">Live</span> <a href="/explainers/robinson-huron-treaty">Robinson Huron Treaty</a> <span>· the annuity settlement, in plain language</span></li>
      <li><span class="fund-stage fund-stage--live">Live</span> <a href="/explainers/massey-solar-project">The Massey solar project</a> <span>· the proposal, the review, the open questions</span></li>
      <li><span class="fund-stage fund-stage--live">Live</span> <a href="/explainers/where-your-data-lives">Where your data lives</a> <span>· where community data physically goes</span></li>
      <li><span class="fund-stage fund-stage--live">Live</span> <a href="/practice/ai-in-coursework">AI in coursework</a> <span>· a working example of responsible AI use</span></li>
      <li><span class="fund-stage fund-stage--live">Live</span> <a href="/news">News</a> <span>· time-stamped updates, newest first</span></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="fund-sec">
    <h2>The fundable next step</h2>
    <div class="fund-body">
      <p>The reach is measured with first-party analytics, no ad-tech. Funding extends the program to more communities and more topics, with each explainer maintained as a living resource rather than left to go stale.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="fund-more">
    <p class="fund-more__k">More from this program</p>
    <div class="fund-more__links">
      <a href="/explainers/massey-solar-project">Massey solar project</a>
      <a href="/explainers/robinson-huron-treaty">Robinson Huron Treaty</a>
      <a href="/news">News</a>
      <a href="/support">Support this program</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</article>
{% endblock %}
